description:
This is a 15 minute workout called '15 Min FULL BODY CALISTHENICS WORKOUT at Home | No Equipment' from the channel Tom Peto Training.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Foundation Builder vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.

Original workout description: Build strength and follow along at home with this 15 minute Calisthenics workout. This is a no equipment full body bodyweight workout using the best Calisthenics exercises for a quick and effective routine. I provide both beginner and more advanced exercise variations within this workout. 

Whether your looking to build strength, or gain muscle this video is a great addition to your Calisthenics training.
